edu.umass.cs.gnsclient.client.util

Class BasicGuidEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.gnsclient.client.util.BasicGuidEntry
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GuidEntry

    public class BasicGuidEntry
extends Object
    This class defines a BasicGuidEntry. This object encapsulates just the information associated with a guid that can be read and written from a GNS server. See also GuidEntry which also contains the private key and cannot be read or written to the GNS.
    Author:
    Westy
